node.title: One person dead in Timaru crash
node.description: Police have confirmed one person has died following a single-vehicle crash in Timaru this afternoon.
node.content:
["Police have confirmed one person has died following a single-vehicle crash in Timaru this afternoon.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Marika Khabazi\n
", "In a statement, Police say they were called to the scene of a crash on Church Street at about 3.40pm.", "The busy street will remain closed while the Serious Crash Unit investigates the scene.", "Police are urging motorists to avoid the area."]
